---
title: Honey & Thyme-Glazed Haloumi with Chermoula Veggie Couscous & Garlic Yoghurt
description: There was complete mayhem when this dish hit our tasting table. With sweet honey and fragrant thyme on warm, salty haloumi,
plus chermoula veggies and pepitas, it disappeared from the bowl in record time. Enjoy!

